                            <comment id="17136241" author="lzljs3620320" created="Tue, 16 Jun 2020 02:20:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;First, I don&apos;t think this is a technical bug, but it can be a user&#160;oriented bug.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The options control the &quot;see the part file&quot; for csv,json are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;rolling-policy.time-interval&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;bucket check interval&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;checkpoint interval&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;As long as one of the three options is not set small, it will not achieve the desired effect.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
